Propaganda Games是一間於2005年成立的電子遊戲開發商，由[[EA加拿大|EA加拿大]]的前僱員組成，並由迪士尼互動工作室擁有<ref name="GS_050419">{{Cite web |url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/disney-scoops-up-avalanche-founds-new-studio/1100-6122500/ |title = Disney scoops up Avalanche, founds new studio |author = Gamespot |date = 2005-04-19 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-05 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6HzF3KGHT?url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/disney-scoops-up-avalanche-founds-new-studio-6122500 |archivedate = 2013-07-09}}</ref>。Propaganda Games主要為迪士尼互動工作室開發動作冒險遊戲，亦負責本作的開發工作<ref name="GS_050419"/>。該開發商的首款遊戲《[[恐龙猎人系列#恐龙猎人_2|恐龍獵人]]》售出超過一百萬份，取得了商業上的成功<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2008/03/26/turoks-dinosaurs-run-rampant-with-more-than-1-million-units-shipped-worldwide |title = Turok's Dinosaurs Run Rampant with More Than 1 Million Units Shipped Worldwide |author = IGN |date = 2008-03-27 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-05 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200906052552/https://www.ign.com/articles/2008/03/26/turoks-dinosaurs-run-rampant-with-more-than-1-million-units-shipped-worldwide |archivedate = 2020-09-06 }}</ref>。在《恐龍獵人》發行後，Propaganda Games隨即著手於有關魔盜王系列的遊戲項目<ref name="G4@Pfister_100514">{{Cite web |url = http://www.g4tv.com/thefeed/blog/post/704687/pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned-interview-propaganda-games-alex-peters/ |title = Pirates of the Caribbean: Armada of the Damned Interview: Propaganda Games' Alex Peters |author = Andrew Pfister |date = 2010-05-14 |publisher = G4 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-05 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130112181043/http://www.g4tv.com/thefeed/blog/post/704687/pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned-interview-propaganda-games-alex-peters/ |archivedate = 2013-01-12}}</ref>。公司副總裁兼總經理丹·塔奇（Dan Tudge）在2010年5月接受訪問時曾表示，這款遊戲是「粉絲們渴望探索的世界」<ref name="G4@Pfister_100514"/>。另外，開發商透露他們編寫了多個腳本來改善遊戲玩法的重點，亦加入了互動選擇系統以塑造遊戲，使玩家的選擇成為遊戲的重要特色<ref name="GameRader@Antista_100514"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2009/05/26/pre-e3-2009-pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned-unveiled |title = Pre-E3 2009: Pirates of the Caribbean: Armada of the Damned Unveiled |author = Hilary Goldstein |date = 2009-05-27 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-05 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025050844/http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/05/26/pre-e3-2009-pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned-unveiled |archivedate = 2012-10-25}}</ref>。

根據遊戲總監亞歷克斯·彼得斯（Alex Peters）的說法，遊戲與電影系列中出現的角色沒有任何關係，更指「開發人員明確表示不想遊戲和電影有關聯」<ref name="GameRader+@Talbot_100211"/>。這種渴望導致詹姆斯·斯特林的出現，一個有著電影角色般的熟悉感、同時又能符合開發人員需求的角色<ref name="GameRader+@Talbot_100211"/>。另外，Propaganda Games為遊戲創作了完全原創的背景樂曲，並把電影的主題曲視為「高雅的歌曲」，僅偶爾在部份場景使用<ref name="IGN@Clements_100511"/>。

在本作的開發過程期間，Propaganda Games還同時開始了《{{tsl|en|Tron: Evolution|創戰紀：進化}}》的開發工作，並在2010年12月發行遊戲<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.gamespot.com/news/tron-evolution-begins-dec-7-6274733 |title = Tron: Evolution begins Dec. 7 |author = Tom Magrino |date = 2010-08-30 |publisher = GameSpot |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121107114528/http://www.gamespot.com/news/tron-evolution-begins-dec-7-6274733 |archivedate = 2012-11-07}}</ref>。2010年10月，迪士尼互動工作室宣布推行Propaganda Games的架構重組計劃，遊戲的開發團隊因而被解僱，但《創戰紀：進化》及其追加下載內容的開發工作則不受影響<ref name="Kotaku@Crecente_101014">{{Cite web |url = https://kotaku.com/pirates-of-the-caribbean-game-canned-as-layoffs-hit-pro-5664021 |title = Pirates of the Caribbean Game Canned as Layoffs Hit Propaganda CONFIRMED |author = Brian Crecente |date = 2010-10-14 |publisher = Kotaku |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130615070634/http://kotaku.com/5664021/rumor-pirates-of-the-caribbean-game-canned-as-layoffs-hit-propaganda |archivedate = 2013-06-15}}</ref>。架構重組令Propaganda Games減少了百多名員工，並需要中止本作的開發工作<ref name="Kotaku@Crecente_101014"/>。在中止開發後，原定用於遊戲內的原創背景樂曲則轉移至2011年發行的《[[樂高神鬼奇航|樂高神鬼奇航]]》內<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.vg247.com/2011/05/13/lego-pirates-uses-music-from-axed-armada-of-the-damned/ |title = LEGO Pirates uses music from axed Armada of the Damned |author = Jessica Citizen |date = 2011-05-13 |publisher = VG247 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110516225910/http://www.vg247.com/2011/05/13/lego-pirates-uses-music-from-axed-armada-of-the-damned/ |archivedate = 2011-05-16}}</ref>。另一方面，負責《創戰紀：進化》的開發團隊同樣受到裁員的影響，但他們仍致力於完成該遊戲的開發工作<ref name="Kotaku@Crecente_101014"/>。然而，《創戰紀：進化》在發行後未能取得商業上的成功，因此迪士尼互動工作室中止了其追加下載內容的開發工作，並關閉了Propaganda Games<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.joystiq.com/2011/01/19/propaganda-games-shuttered/ |title = Propaganda Games shuttered |author = Ben Gilbert |date = 2011-01-19 |publisher = Joystiq |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121118190037/http://www.joystiq.com/2011/01/19/propaganda-games-shuttered/ |archivedate = 2012-11-18}}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
當迪士尼互動娛樂工作室在2009年[[E3電子娛樂展|E3電子娛樂展]]上公開此遊戲時<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2009/05/27/disney-interactive-studios-announces-pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned |title = Disney Interactive Studios Announces Pirates of the Caribbean: Armada of the Damned |author = IGN |date = 2009-05-28 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6HzFlt0cP?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/05/27/disney-interactive-studios-announces-pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned |archivedate = 2013-07-09}}</ref>，大多數遊戲記者及評論家都給予正面評價。[[IGN|IGN]]的戴蒙·哈特菲爾德（Daemon Hatfield）把遊戲形容為「一款很有前途的角色扮演遊戲」，又指「即使遊戲打著魔盜王的名號，但它仍然是一款獨立遊戲，是一款可讓玩家創造屬於自己的海盜角色，並在加勒比海中徘徊以尋求名利的冒險遊戲」<ref name="IGN@Hatfield_100519"/>。[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar]]的克里斯·安妮斯塔（Chris Antista）則稱讚遊戲玩法，並將其與[[刺客教條系列|刺客教條系列]]進行比較。安妮斯塔又指開發人員極大地在遊戲內保留了電影的精神，且沒有執著於重現玩家早已在大銀幕上看到的畫面<ref name="GameRader@Antista_100514"/>。

《[[官方Xbox雜誌|官方Xbox雜誌]]》的一位編輯指「魔盜王系列有一個美好的開始，隨後卻逐漸陷入平庸，但在續集內竟出現了有著觸手的卡拉肯」，故推測任何一款把故事設定在第一部電影之前的魔盜王遊戲都可能很棒<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.oxm.co.uk/11968/previews/pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned/ |title = Pirates of the Caribbean: Armada of the Damned |author = Official Xbox Magazine |date = 2009-07-15 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6HzFqLWTh?url=http://www.oxm.co.uk/11968/previews/pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned/ |archivedate = 2013-07-09}}</ref>。《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》的馬特·米勒（Matt Miller）對遊戲有著深刻的印象，稱讚其語音和戰鬥系統有如[[質量效應系列|質量效應系列]]般優秀。米勒更指「我們並沒有對參與海盜聚會寄予很高的期望，但是對遊戲的潛力感到驚訝」<ref name="GameInformer@Miller_100622"/>。[[Joystiq|Joystiq]]的邁克·施拉姆（Mike Schramm）把遊戲與《[[神鬼寓言|神鬼寓言]]》作比較，並指遊戲的戰鬥很紮實但有點淺薄，而遊戲畫面及抛光效果則很不錯<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.joystiq.com/2010/06/20/preview-pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned |title = Preview: Pirates of the Caribbean: Armada of the Damned |author = Mike Schramm |date = 2010-06-20 |publisher = Joystiq |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100625055737/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/06/20/preview-pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned |archivedate = 2010-06-25}}</ref>。

在遊戲預計發行日期前的數個月，迪士尼互動娛樂工作室宣佈裁減Propaganda Games的員工並中止開發遊戲，當時不少遊戲記者都感到失望。IGN的瑞安·克萊門茨（Ryan Clements）表示遺憾，又指玩家因此而無法在現時認識到該遊戲的潛力<ref name="IGN@Clements_101015">{{Cite web |url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2010/10/14/pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned-cancelled |title = Pirates of the Caribbean: Armada of the Damned Cancelled |author = Ryan Clements |date = 2010-10-15 |publisher = IGN |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6HzG5PApq?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2010/10/14/pirates-of-the-caribbean-armada-of-the-damned-cancelled |archivedate = 2013-07-09}}</ref>。賈斯汀·托威爾（Justin Towell）為GamesRadar撰寫文章時提到他對迪士尼的決定感到沮喪，並指迪士尼沒有理由完全放棄一款即將完成開發工作的遊戲<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.gamesradar.com/its-a-crying-shame-that-the-new-pirates-of-the-caribbean-game-has-been-cancelled-seriously/ |title = It's a crying shame that the new Pirates of the Caribbean game has been cancelled. Seriously |author = Justin Towell |date = 2010-10-15 |publisher = GamesRadar+ |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6HzGAKyzU?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/its-a-crying-shame-that-the-new-pirates-of-the-caribbean-game-has-been-cancelled-seriously/ |archivedate = 2013-07-09}}</ref>。《Game Informer》的傑夫·馬爾基法瓦（Jeff Marchiafava）亦對遊戲中止開發感到悲傷，並表示「沮喪的海盜會發出怎樣的聲音？因為我們現時打算發出這種聲音」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/10/14/disney-confirms-armada-of-the-damned-cancellation.aspx |title = Disney Confirms Armada Of The Damned Cancellation |author = Jeff Marchiafava |date = 2010-10-14 |publisher = Game Informer |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-06 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6HzGDlT6o?url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/10/14/disney-confirms-armada-of-the-damned-cancellation.aspx |archivedate = 2013-07-09}}</ref>。

